<paragraph blockId="57.[144,1104,1583,1678]" pageId="57" pageNumber="632">Approximate body length: (11.4–20.7); maximum width of head: (3.4–4.5); intertegular distance: (3.5–5.4); length of forewing with tegula: (10.8–16.1).</paragraph>
